    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repterra是一款基地建造与生存RTS，背景设定在被恐龙占领的世界。管理你的殖民地，对抗巨型恐龙群。繁殖和骑乘恐龙，解锁永久升级，为人类重夺世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/c321449df659d11cb0e2ff312188eabf.poster.avif?t=1771498266\" width=596 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/c321449df659d11cb0e2ff312188eabf.webm?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/c321449df659d11cb0e2ff312188eabf.mp4?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >庞大殖民地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立庞大殖民地至关重要。构筑防线、搭建生产线、建设强力电网，为前哨提供能源。每个建筑都让你更强大，迎接无尽恐龙浪潮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/4fb6a2c03f28b8f2685ebcc90a91351f.poster.avif?t=1771498266\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/4fb6a2c03f28b8f2685ebcc90a91351f.webm?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/4fb6a2c03f28b8f2685ebcc90a91351f.mp4?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐龙骑乘</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分配士兵、工程师或驯兽师骑乘你的恐龙！每种人类/恐龙组合都有强大独特的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/1d064688630e8c4389a0957b08e7b451.poster.avif?t=1771498266\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/1d064688630e8c4389a0957b08e7b451.webm?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/1d064688630e8c4389a0957b08e7b451.mp4?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >繁殖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将一对雄性/雌性恐龙放入繁殖站，让大自然自行发挥！后代可能会带来惊喜。支持基因变异杂交。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驯服</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用食物、诱惑或其他手段引诱敌方恐龙。驯服后，它们将为你而战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄单位</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可升级的英雄单位拥有特殊的主动和被动技能，死亡后会重生。升级你的英雄并通过基因突变自定义。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >派系</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5个派系，每个派系有独特单位、特权和英雄。每个派系主打不同玩法：资源、机动、科技、驯服或战斗。选择适合你策略的派系征服世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/02efc59b581f1d1622d8b5102ed4d9b3.poster.avif?t=1771498266\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/02efc59b581f1d1622d8b5102ed4d9b3.webm?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268620/extras/02efc59b581f1d1622d8b5102ed4d9b3.mp4?t=1771498266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1963年，探险家在印度洋发现了一座被磁异常隐藏的未知岛屿，上面生活着三叠纪恐龙。盗猎者把它们卖给富人做宠物，长期囚禁令恐龙变得凶猛，逃逸事件被权贵掩盖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到90年代，逃出的恐龙迅速繁殖，数百万只恐龙肆虐地球，摧毁人口和基础设施，使大片区域变成无人区，全球供应链崩溃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在，人类必须收复失地。作为特遣队一员，你的任务是控制恐龙，为人类重建铺路。文明的未来掌握在你手中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的繁殖、骑乘、驯服机制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5大派系各具特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加载时可选修改游戏的特权</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久解锁点数与商店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义英雄单位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战役模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的生存模式，含解锁与元进程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10万+恐龙，流畅运行60帧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种单位、恐龙和建筑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成就与Steam云存档</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4K高清复古预渲染画风</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收复地球，用恐龙科技对抗恐龙！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
